Machine learning uses algorithms that learn patterns from data using:

Statistical methods
Feature engineering
Mathematical optimization

Examples:
Decision Trees
SVM
Random Forest
K-Means

Deep Learning (DL)
Deep learning uses:
Multi-layer neural networks
Large datasets
High computational power

to automatically learn features and patterns.
Examples:
CNN
RNN
Transformer
Autoencoder

Main Difference

Machine Learning
Humans manually design features.
Input Data
   ↓
Feature Extraction (Human-designed)
   ↓
ML Algorithm
   ↓
Prediction

Deep Learning
System learns features automatically.
Input Data
   ↓
Deep Neural Network
   ↓
Automatic Feature Learning
   ↓
Prediction

